modern technological equipment such as refrigerators with interactive screens, TV, PC, tablet ... at the home of the child could himself confessed dream Convention, from which donors can monitor and interact by sending an appropriate gift or send written messages, encouraging the students&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-24/1487916525-cung-samsung-ket-noi-yeu-thuong--5-.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Phan Anh đ&amp;oacute;ng vai &amp;ldquo;người vận chuyển&amp;rdquo; trong h&amp;agrave;nh tr&amp;igrave;nh Kết nối y&amp;ecirc;u thương - 5&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Phan Anh favorite: &quot;The advantage of applying technology in this project is the financial management system of effective, transparent information display, overcoming barriers of distance in geography and time. Do not just stop at the physical gifts, the children here are very happy to receive the message of love, words of encouragement and shared from donors .... &quot;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Not only represents nationwide philanthropists donated necessities and gifts are &quot;designed&quot; according to the dreams of each individual child, the program also brings the game fun and colorful repertoire, help children with memorable moments&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-24/1487916525-cung-samsung-ket-noi-yeu-thuong--7-.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Phan Anh đ&amp;oacute;ng vai &amp;ldquo;người vận chuyển&amp;rdquo; trong h&amp;agrave;nh tr&amp;igrave;nh Kết nối y&amp;ecirc;u thương - 7&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Samsum Connect works on the principle of transparency of information and personalized user experience. Information on shelters and activities contribute regularly updated, constantly, publicly.&amp;nbsp;Transparency, convenience, openness and &quot;digitize&quot; all data is the difference of the project Connected Love.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;After a month of implementing the project in Da Nang, Samsum Connect loved connected between the 38 donors and 48 children at the orphanage, donation amount up to 700 million includes the entire basic necessities they need in everyday life as well as their wishes have been listened and contributed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Sharing more about this program, representatives Samsum Vietnam said: &quot;This project is dedicated and our most meaningful. As with Samsum, technology is not just technology. Technology must be humane and supports interactive, linking people together, help create a brighter future. We believe that, together, we will create more is the deep human connection and hope you will continue to accompany us in the journey of love connection in Dien Bien on May 03 / 2017 to &quot;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 0, '', 0, '', '', '1487924599.jpg', '24022017152318', 0, 632, 1, 2, '2017-02-24 15:23:18', NULL, 142, NULL, 1),
(1721, 'Hanoi proposed transfer  dormitory trillions  of social housing', 'Hanoi-proposed-transfer--dormitory-trillions--of-social-housing', '', '1', '<p>Hanoi Department of Construction has proposed converting two buildings A2, A3 of student housing projects Phap Van - Tu Hiep (Hoang Mai district) into social housing.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;Student housing project at this scale 20-story towers 6 (A1, A5, A6 were put to use). Currently, the construction of A4 no lack of space, the A2, A3 incomplete and stopped now deployed in the primary construction.&amp;nbsp;Based on the partnership agreement with the general contractor to complete the project objectives, avoid debt, Department of Civil Engineering has allowed convert the A2, A3 from student housing into social housing for sale and for rent in the form of socialization.&amp;nbsp;The enterprise is assigned with the responsibility to repay the state the funds invested for the category A2, A3, 340 billion, to be the source of repayment for the completed volume of the A1, A5, A6 (approximately 233.8 billion).&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-20/1487554000-nha_o_xa_hoi_gia_100_trieu.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Chung cư si&amp;ecirc;u rẻ chỉ 100 triệu đồng: Nếu H&amp;agrave; Nội &amp;ldquo;bật đ&amp;egrave;n xanh&amp;rdquo;&amp;hellip; - 1&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 0, '', 0, '', '', '1487814033.jpg', '23022017084032', 0, 626, 1, 2, '2017-02-23 08:40:32', NULL, 142, NULL, 1),
