(1728, 'Booming supply of affordable housing', 'Booming-supply-of-affordable-housing', '', '1', '<p>Real estate market in 2017 is forecast strong growth segment of affordable housing. This is the segment in line with the needs of the poor majority and stimulus with preferential credit line will be deployed for social housing.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;A series of large enterprises in the real estate giant promises to supply affordable housing segment in 2017. In particular, many corporations to build affordable housing at the position of the Hanoi Gia Lam district (near 300 ha) and Dan Phuong district (130 hectares); HCMC has projects in District 7 (20ha) and District 9 (nearly 300 ha); Hung Yen has 1 500 ha project near Ecopark township. Accordingly, this product consists of condominiums from 22 to 25 floors; 35m2 to 90m2; The average selling price of between 13 and 19 million / m2. Vingroup vowed to build approximately 2-300 thousand apartments with brand Vincity cost between 700 million / unit. Muong Thanh Group also recently sold and put into use thousands of apartments in 2017 in the urban area, Thanh Ha (Ha Dong, Hanoi) for less than 10 million / m2; Capital Company also offers hundreds of cheap apartments 15-17 million / m2 in projects Ecohome Welfare (Long Bien District, Hanoi) ...&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-03/1486083756-5a_vlnk.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;B&amp;ugrave;ng nổ nguồn cung nh&amp;agrave; ở gi&amp;aacute; rẻ - 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Social housing will be pumped 1.000 billion in concessional loans in 2017&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Mr. Pham Thanh Hung, Deputy Chairman Cengroup analysis, affordable housing segment, aimed at people who buy just a house to stay. This segment is completely different from the premium segment, as buyers consider a lot of profits, interest rates ... Meanwhile, in 2016 the supply of high real estate segment abundant, efficient exploitation fo