(1729, 'New social housing to meet the needs of 28&amp;permil; of the people', 'New-social-housing-to-meet-the-needs-of-28%-of-the-people', '', '1', '<p>According to the Ministry of Construction, from 2009 to now, there are nearly 500,000 new settlement housing for workers and low-income earners, while the targets set out in the strategy for national development are 250,000 housing units they&hellip;</p>', '&lt;p&gt;Report online at the national conference on social housing, housing for workers 7/12 morning, the Minister of Construction Pham Hong Ha said that from 2009 to date, the country has completed investment 179 construction projects, the construction scale of about 71,150 apartments, equivalent to approximately 3.7 million m2 of social housing (NOXH) in urban areas and industrial zones, contribute to solving the home to nearly 500,000 workers and low-income people. Total investment for the project said on approximately 25,900 billion (97 social housing projects for workers, 82 projects NOXH for people with low incomes). Currently local authorities are continuing to implement 191 projects; including 70 project workers NOXH, 121 social housing projects for low-income people) to scale construction 163 800 apartments, a total investment of about 71 800 billion.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Results disbursed 30,000 billion credit package to support housing, as of 31/10/2016, has signed loan commitments are 32 841 billion and disbursed 28588.7 billion (87.05% ). In particular, already signed loan commitments 56 181 households, in the amount of 27 480 billion; 56 181 disbursed to households, in the amount of 23 226 billion (84.52% loan commitments); has committed to lend 51 projects, was disbursed in the amount of 5.361 billion. According to the Ministry of Construction, the development NOXH for the poor and low-income urban areas, industrial park workers did not meet the demand, the targets set in the Strategic National housing development.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class