(1731, 'Barca: Messi signed a new contract, &amp;quot;processing&amp;quot; of 100 million pounds of Manchest', 'Barca:-Messi-signed-a-new-contract,-"processing"-of-100-million-pounds-of-Manchester-City', '', '1', '<p>A legendary Camp Nou disclosure, Messi has officially put pen to contract extension with Barcelona.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;Recently, Barcelona\'s performance is erratic which is pulled by doubts about the future of Messi. Many news that the Argentine striker will break up the Nou Camp when the season is not over after the team needs on wages.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-23/1487813792-500messi-2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Barca: Messi k&amp;yacute; hợp đồng mới, &amp;amp;#34;ch&amp;ecirc;&amp;amp;#34; 100 triệu bảng của Man City - 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;Messi has renewed a contract with Barca?&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The most ideal destination for Messi as Man City. Here, the England team ready rich pay well while Leo was working with former mentor Guardiola. In addition, to convince people Barca release, BLD Man City ready on the table negotiating 100 million pounds. However, all the above information will only stop on the report. Recently, the former striker Hristo Stoichkov has revealed the complete opposite developments at the Nou Camp. Bulgarian football legend who confirmed Messi has agreed to stay in Barca and even put pen to contract extension from 6 months ago.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;However, all the above information will only stop on the report. Recently, the former striker Hristo Stoichkov has revealed the complete opposite developments at the Nou Camp. Bulgarian football legend who confirmed Messi has agreed to stay in Barca and even put pen to contract extension from 6 months ago. &quot;Barca are still doing their job well. There will be no change at all in the near future. Do not deny the results in Paris is bad, but can not judge a team through a g