(1764, 'Top 3 Highlights motor technology', 'Top-3-Highlights-motor-technology', '', '1', '<p>Find out how technology featured motorcycles</p>', '&lt;p&gt;1. High-tech Applications&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-20/1487585908-14874739623200-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Top 10 c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ m&amp;ocirc; t&amp;ocirc; nổi bật trong v&amp;ograve;ng 30 năm qua - 1&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;High technology appear in almost everything, such as helmet Skully AR-1, it integrates the screen HUD (Heads Up Display). This screen displays vehicle speed, outside temperature, connected to the smartphone via bluetooth ...&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;2. The electric motorcycle&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-20/1487585908-148747396223132-3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Top 10 c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ m&amp;ocirc; t&amp;ocirc; nổi bật trong v&amp;ograve;ng 30 năm qua - 3&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Difficulties when controlling a battery-powered car in the long road has been resolved with DSR Zero models. It can go 100 miles on a single charge.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;3. Braking System Anti-lock Braking (antilock Braking Systems)&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-20/1487585909-148747396224185-7.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Top 10 c&amp;ocirc;ng nghệ m&amp;ocirc; t&amp;ocirc; nổi bật trong v&amp;ograve;ng 30 năm qua - 7&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Just like Traction Control, ABS launched quite soon, it is applied for the first time on the cars of Mercedes-Benz in 1978, then also be used on other vehicles including motorcycles. It was invented by Bosch and the company is now a mandatory system of the vehicle in some countries. This is a necessary safety technology for vehicles, reduce speed or stop the car in case of necessity.&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 0, '', 0, '', '', '1487927154.jpg', '24022017160553', 0, 629, 1, 2, '2017-02-24 16:05:54', NULL, 142, NULL, 1),
(1765, 'Yamaha YZF-R3 stick bug was summoned in Vietnam', 'Yamaha-YZF-R3-stick-bug-was-summoned-in-Vietnam', '', '1', '<p>Yamaha YZF-R3 cars encountered two errors is the fuel tank bracket and the electrical system has been corrupted.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;Today, Yamaha Motor has officially releases the program summon YZF-R3 880 cars to fix errors that may affect the operation of the vehicle.&amp;nbsp;The Yamaha YZF-R3 units are in the affected area are manufactured from January to March 06/2016 06/2015 with chassis numbers range from MH3RH0760FK001001 to MH3RH0760GK001880.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-24/1487903082-148790297447277-48.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;D&amp;iacute;nh lỗi Yamaha YZF-R3 bị triệu hồi tại Việt Nam - 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Yamaha YZF-R3 in Vietnam have also been summoned.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The cause of the recall is due to a fault in the car YZF-R3 can affect the operation of the vehicle. The first is the rack position can touch the fuel tank fuel tank bracket by size mismatch. On some vehicles, engine vibration actuator to operate the fuel tank, leading to the location of the fuel tank bottom welding can be broken.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The worst case will occur gasoline flowing. The second error can occur as impurities water flow into the lock and deposited on the switch leads to the ability of abrasion resistance spot. Worst case, the current can be interrupted and can be stalled car when the car is running.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-24/1487903344-14879032411156-47.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;D&amp;iacute;nh lỗi Yamaha YZF-R3 bị triệu hồi tại Việt Nam - 2&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Yamaha\'s side said, as of the present time the company has not received any incidents that occur due to this cause. However, to ensure the interests of consumers, the company decided to recall all of the vehicles in question to handle area thoroughly.&amp;nbsp;Accordingly, as of 23 May 02 2017,&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Yamaha Motor began deploying the free replacement of parts in the area summoned by parts has been improved in the system nationwide Yamaha Sports Shop. After completion of the replacement agent staff stamping letters &quot;Y&quot; to the right of the frame to confirm the completion of the repair.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 0, '', 0, '', '', '1487927319.jpg', '24022017160838', 0, 629, 1, 2, '2017-02-24 16:08:38', NULL, 142, NULL, 1);

